title: #92Noon! Russo/WildJoe/Hentges/Gleeman
description: First hour includes Russo on the Wild loss, and some opinions on the awful allegations against Jeff Gladney...Wild Joe Odonnell joins after calling last night's 5-4 Wild loss, SCSU Huskies forward Sam Hentges calls in from Pittsburgh midway thru, then it's Gleeman during the final hour!
